metadata.name: LB4HFP #1
metadata.description:
Attention all highflyers! Looking for the ultimate soundtrack to fuel your productivity and creativity? Look no further than Lofi Beats! Our unique blend of short hip-hop and sample-influenced funky loops are designed to get your head nodding and your creative juices flowing. Whether you need to focus on a project, get in the zone for a workout, or just relax and unwind, Lofi Beats has got you covered.

The Blue Print consists of:
15 different Beats
11 Basslines
14 Percussion Tracks
26 Melody Tracks
18 Addon Tracks

2 Legendary Versions hidden in it
